| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0372 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 65a65f40-38f4-5dd5-99f8-e732c7b36065"
